                <section className="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-900/40 to-indigo-900/40 border border-pink-500/20 p-8 rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden group">
                  <div className="relative z-10">
                    <h1 className="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">定制学习规划</h1>
                    <p className="text-pink-100/60 max-w-md mb-6">点击下方按钮，AI 将根据你最近的笔记内容，为你量身定制最佳的学习方案。</p>
